title: Botswana Gross Fixed Capital Formation
description: Gross Fixed Capital Formation in Botswana decreased to 10177 BWP Million in the second quarter of 2022 from 10237 BWP Million in the first quarter of 2022. Gross Fixed Capital Formation in Botswana averaged 12357.57 BWP Million from 2002 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 27689.01 BWP Million in the fourth quarter of 2013 and a record low of 8459 BWP Million in the second quarter of 2020. This page provides - Botswana Gross Fixed Capital Formation - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Bank Of Botswana
